Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:36.98,Umaru_Ep_Title,title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(504,1)}Episode 8   {\fs20}Umaru and Christmas and New Year's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.25,0:01:53.63,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan! It's snowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:01:59.34,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}thought{\i0} it seemed cold. It's snowing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.34,0:02:02.01,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's all white outside! \NDo you think it'll stick?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.50,0:02:04.72,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to go to the supermarket today,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.19,0:02:08.06,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,but I probably shouldn't go out in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.22,0:02:12.39,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Then since I'm the \Nexpert on being a shut-in,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.39,0:02:15.48,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll plan the ideal day off for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:17.03,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Now, sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:18.95,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,You're just going to play games, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:21.91,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I was \Nplanning to bring out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:23.41,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Bring out? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.32,0:02:26.41,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,The kotatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:29.15,umaruun_02:27,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,377)}Umaruun
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.30,0:02:30.36,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.36,0:02:33.17,Umaru_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we need to do first, Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.62,0:02:35.88,Umaru_Italics,onii,0000,0000,0000,,She only gets motivated at times like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.93,0:02:37.80,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,First...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.41,0:02:40.70,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,Clean up the mess you've made.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:42.39,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.69,0:02:44.68,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,One, two. One, two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.68,0:02:46.95,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just move it all to one corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:53.91,Umaru_Italics,onii,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... What would happen \Nto her if I weren't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.91,0:02:56.61,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get serious next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:06.33,mogumogu_03:04,book,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}Disembodied Head\N{\c&HA64BFF&}Mogu Mogu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:25.21,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:33.36,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.36,0:03:34.35,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:36.96,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,Don't dive in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:49.00,Umaru_Italics,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a confined space, \Nyet why does it feel like heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:53.55,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we've got the kotatsu out, \NI've gotta bring over some stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:57.60,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:06.08,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,This is my paradise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:10.84,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,I should have bought some mandarins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.84,0:04:12.27,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go get some tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:13.87,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Umaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,0:04:22.57,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,She already fell asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:28.20,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,They say it's easy to catch a cold if \Nyou let your upper body get cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:31.33,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Umaru, wake up. You'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.62,0:04:44.94,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll wake her up in an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:55.35,mikan_04:51,boxes,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(840,1)}Clementines
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.49,0:04:57.23,Umaru_Main,kiri,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:04:59.88,Umaru_Main,kiri,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the way! Go sleep in your own room!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:01.98,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,Just one more hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.09,0:05:04.43,zuzashaan_05:02,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Zuzashaan
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:24.47,Umaru_Time_Setting,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(403,1)}December 24th
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:32.07,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:35.23,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas... It is the celebration of winter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:39.86,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure people will go out \Nat night to see the the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:42.88,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,However, I will not be \Nleaving the house at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:48.29,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Today, we will have a lazy little \Nparty, while eating cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:50.62,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:53.87,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder when Onii-chan will be home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.61,0:06:06.38,Umaru_Time_Setting,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(545,1)}Overtime on Christmas...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:08.07,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:09.74,Umaru_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is wrong with this company?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:12.14,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,I know how you feel, \Nbut don't say it out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:16.02,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Taihei. Let's quit this stupid company!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:18.77,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that much, so just tough it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:21.44,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,How is this "not that much"?! How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:24.65,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,This sucks. I want to go back \Nto how things used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:27.53,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,When we were young and free...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:30.77,Umaru_Main,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't just run away from reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.77,0:06:33.68,Umaru_Main,tai,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, what are \Nyou looking at during work?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:35.16,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:36.81,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Santa outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.81,0:06:38.40,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna wear one with me, Taihei?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:41.71,Umaru_Main,kanau,0000,0000,0000,,It's not going to come the same \Nday you order it, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:43.04,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,True...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.56,0:06:45.70,Umaru_Main,kanau,0000,0000,0000,,Have you finished your checks?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:50.75,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Chief Kanau...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.75,0:06:53.18,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was just taking a little break...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:57.69,Umaru_Main,kanau,0000,0000,0000,,You can quit at any time, A-f-ro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:07:02.40,Umaru_Main,kanau,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about this, Taihei. \NI know it's Christmas and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:05.11,Umaru_Main,tai,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.39,0:07:08.35,Umaru_Main,kanau,0000,0000,0000,,Your proposal the other day was spectacular.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.35,0:07:11.07,Umaru_Main,kanau,0000,0000,0000,,The higher-ups that didn't pass it are shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:13.70,Umaru_Main,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:16.70,Umaru_Main,kanau,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you have any plans today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:19.87,Umaru_Main,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I can't see the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:25.79,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Kirie-chan hasn't tweeted anything today...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:29.29,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,And Ebina-chan went to visit her parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:32.12,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she's out with her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:02.04,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wonder who that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:04.84,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan would have a key.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.06,0:08:18.60,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan! And Kirie-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:20.12,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:22.51,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,I just ran into Kirie-chan over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.51,0:08:24.36,Umaru_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys didn't have plans together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:25.44,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:28.21,Umaru_Main,kiri,0000,0000,0000,,I-I bought a present for you, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:31.78,octosanta_08:29,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,1)}Octopus\NSanta
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:35.17,Umaru_Main,kiri,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why are you dressed as Santa, Onii-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:37.99,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I went and bought \None with my coworker,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:40.20,Umaru_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and he said I might as well just wear it home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.86,0:08:46.46,Umaru_Italics,ebina,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas, Umaru-chan! \NAkita is covered in snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:51.11,Umaru_Main,kiri,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Master! You're a reindeer today!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:52.46,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:57.08,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:08:59.97,honba_08:57,house sign,0000,0000,0000,,Honba
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:04.14,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,Heya, Kirie! Santa's home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.45,0:09:05.19,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:13.94,newyear's_09:08,sign,0000,0000,0000,,New Year's Eve Across the Country
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:11.48,Umaru_Italics,lady,0000,0000,0000,,The year is coming to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:15.24,Umaru_Italics,lady,0000,0000,0000,,What was the most memorable \Npart of the year for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:16.36,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Taihei?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:18.74,Umaru_Main,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Well, a lot happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:20.92,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,For me, it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.92,0:09:24.58,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,Dressing up as Santa and waiting \Nfor my sister to come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:27.06,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that really recent?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:28.92,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:31.71,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,She beat the crap out \Nof me when she got home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.57,0:09:35.55,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,For me, that steak was really yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:36.59,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna eat it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:38.59,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, sometime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:40.32,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna eat ramen, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:42.97,Umaru_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,When Ebina-chan comes home, let's go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:44.48,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,Who's Ebina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:47.81,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,She's my friend. \NShe's back in Akita right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:50.12,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Akita, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:51.27,Umaru_Main,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Ayup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.74,0:09:56.35,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, the first time \NEbina-chan came over was this year, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.35,0:09:58.53,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,A lot happened this year, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:09:59.93,Umaru_Main,kiri,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.40,0:10:04.88,Umaru_Italics,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. I became friends with \NKirie-chan this year, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:06.91,Umaru_Italics,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should have invited her over today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.22,0:10:09.63,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,My little sister's so violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:12.13,Umaru_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, I'm sure she's \Njust being shy around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:13.16,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:17.38,Umaru_Italics,guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's not yet time to ring the \NNew Year's bell, but take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:19.45,Umaru_Italics,guy,0000,0000,0000,,There are already this many people in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:19.91,shuba_10:19,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,333)}Shuba
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.58,0:10:23.99,shubaan_10:22,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,284)}Shubaan
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:26.89,Umaru_Italics,sylph,0000,0000,0000,,I got to ring it first!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:29.87,Umaru_Italics,guy bg,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hey, give me back my mic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:31.06,Umaru_Italics,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,I-I hung out with Sylphyn-san a lot, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:37.28,shrine_10:31,sign,0000,0000,0000,,First Shrine Visits\NAround the Country
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:34.40,Umaru_Italics,lady,0000,0000,0000,,This is live footage from around the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:37.28,Umaru_Italics,lady,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's lining up, \Neven though it's so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:40.28,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that's way too many people for \Nthe first shrine visit of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:42.36,Umaru_Main,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Should we all go later?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.36,0:10:44.18,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:46.29,Umaru_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to count down in the kotatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:48.29,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gaki no Chikai{\i0} is okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.26,0:10:56.00,Umaru_Main,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Umaru, are you going to stay \Nup until the countdown?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:59.49,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! I'm so pumped, \Nlike I was going to see the first sunrise!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:05.85,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then. I guess it's time to get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:10.07,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Are we going to do something, Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.07,0:11:12.43,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be... the samba?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.43,0:11:13.98,Umaru_Main,tai,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of way is that \Nto start a new year?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:17.86,yakitori_11:16,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(149,1)}Yakitori
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.89,0:11:17.86,Umaru_Main,bomb,0000,0000,0000,,Yakitori!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:19.24,edamame_11:18,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(147,1)}Edamame
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:19.24,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,Edamame!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:20.86,kaki-pi_11:19,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(112,1)}Kakinotane
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:20.86,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,Kakinotane!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.48,0:11:23.98,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing says ringing in \Nthe New Year like drinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:28.18,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,Bomber, I appreciate you \Npreparing all of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:32.45,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,but I wasn't going to drink \Nthis year, since Umaru is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:42.47,bringles_11:40,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(107,1)}Bringles
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:42.47,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Bringles!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:43.84,sweetbreads_11:42,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(112,1)}Sweet\NBreads
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:43.84,sponge_11:42,left,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(112,1)}Fluffy Steamed Egg Bun
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:43.84,melon_11:42,middle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(112,1)}Soft Melon Bun
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:43.84,red_11:42,right,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(112,1)}Coarse Anko Bun
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:43.84,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet breads!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:46.22,lacto_11:43,brown,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(196,1)}Lacto Ice\N{\fs20}Hyper Cup\N{\fs18}Chocolate
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:46.22,icecream_11:43,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(110,1)}Ice Cream
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:45.41,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ice cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:46.22,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:49.22,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing says ringing in \Nthe New Year like cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:50.85,Umaru_Main,both,0000,0000,0000,,Those are all colas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:55.48,Umaru_Main,bomb,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this cola's all red. \NAnd there's a clear one, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:11:59.93,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,I picked them out specifically \Nfor New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:09.49,ranking_12:00,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(481,1)}Umaru Ranking
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:09.49,ranks_12:00,ranks,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(481,1)}1:               {\c&HEEADA8&}Cola\N{\c&H6283DD&}2:   {\c&HEEADA8&}Melon Soda\N{\c&H6283DD&}3:  {\c&HEEADA8&}Lemon Soda\N{\c&H6283DD&}4:     {\c&HEEADA8&}Plain Soda\N{\c&H6283DD&}5:     {\c&HEEADA8&}Ginger Ale
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.39,0:12:03.08,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,The best pairing with snacks is, of course, cola.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:07.94,points_12:00,umaru sign,0000,0000,0000,,Points
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:05.18,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Though, the sweetness of melon soda
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:07.89,Umaru_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,brings out the saltiness in the \Nsnacks, making it the runner-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:09.50,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,She started explaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:20.96,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan has given his blessing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.96,0:12:22.40,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,Let's party!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:24.64,Umaru_Main,umaru bg,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Party time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.12,0:12:24.93,Umaru_Italics,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I didn't say anything yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.48,0:12:31.88,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Your beer snacks are like actual food, Bomber.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.88,0:12:34.44,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,Beer snacks aren't just snack foods, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:41.15,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,Yum! I've never had yakitori and \Npotato chips together before!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.87,0:12:45.03,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,The meat and potato chips \Nare melting in my mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:46.91,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,Eat the green onions, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:51.79,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Eating ice cream after kakinotane is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:53.63,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, it's chocolate flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:55.79,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,And the textures are different, so it's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:04.84,Umaru_Main,both,0000,0000,0000,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:08.25,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, eat up! Eat up! Wow, this is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.25,0:13:10.35,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,This is great! Let's have another!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:25.84,Umaru_Main,tai,0000,0000,0000,,And then I told the section chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:30.87,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,Is she asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:31.74,Umaru_Main,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, she's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:35.11,Umaru_Main,bomb,0000,0000,0000,,You sure we shouldn't wake \Nher up for the countdown?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:36.57,Umaru_Main,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Let's let her sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:05.86,hny_14:03,door,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,433)}Happy New Year
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:14.82,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,The best thing about New Year's \Nis that I can openly laze around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.82,0:14:18.42,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go to a world \Nwhere New Year's just loops.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:26.05,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:32.55,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,Umaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.43,0:14:34.81,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:39.81,hny_14:03,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.59,0:14:38.53,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember what you promised me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.53,0:14:39.81,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Promised?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:43.31,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,It was in the latter half of November.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.31,0:14:44.98,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:47.44,nov_14:44,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(279,1)}Latter Half of\NNovember
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:47.44,Umaru_Flashback,onii,0000,0000,0000,,Umaru! The room's a mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:52.56,Umaru_Flashback,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,There's not much time left in this year, \Nso I'll do it all at once next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.56,0:14:54.28,Umaru_Flashback,onii,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it all at once! Do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.73,0:14:58.71,Umaru_Flashback,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Onii-chan! I'll \Nget serious starting next year!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.47,0:15:00.75,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,You remember that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.18,0:15:03.59,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I did say that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:09.59,months_15:04,sign,0000,0000,0000,,New Year January\NNew Year February\NNew Year March
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:09.59,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,The "next year" when I was gonna \Nget serious has actually come!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:11.89,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,I remember it as clear as day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:13.94,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't lie to me, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:17.40,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,I-I did indeed say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.40,0:15:20.60,zawa_15:17,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(350,500)}Psst Psst
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:22.05,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,However, I would like you to \Nrecall that I never specified
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.05,0:15:24.48,Umaru_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,an actual date or place, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:26.00,Umaru_Main,tai,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.66,0:15:30.40,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I don't have a choice... \NOkay, I'll clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:32.89,Umaru_Main,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you can clean when we get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:34.53,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Are we going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.84,0:15:36.42,Umaru_Main,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go for the year's first shrine visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:39.91,tagoshrine_15:36,banners,0000,0000,0000,,Tago Shrine
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:44.42,potatoes_15:42,yellored,0000,0000,0000,,Piping Hot\N{\c&H424DE7&}Buttered Potatoes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:48.92,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,There're so many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:49.80,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:50.97,Umaru_Main,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:52.93,Umaru_Main,girl2,0000,0000,0000,,Really? A peace sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.15,0:15:59.56,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,Umaru, did you want to \Ncome in a kimono, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:01.67,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,No. Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:03.08,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:05.28,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Fortune slips!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.28,0:16:07.37,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see who has better luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.97,0:16:10.89,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you take interest when \Nthere's a gambling aspect...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:13.07,luck_16:11,big,0000,0000,0000,,Luck: Good Luck to Come
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:15.25,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you get, Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.25,0:16:16.34,Umaru_Main,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Slightly good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.34,0:16:19.28,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Is that better than "good luck to come"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.28,0:16:20.30,Umaru_Main,tai,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.97,0:16:32.47,Umaru_Main,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Here. For an offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.75,0:16:40.76,Umaru_Main,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:57.49,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,What did you wish for, Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:17:00.14,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,It's more likely to come \Ntrue if you don't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:00.87,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:01.83,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:05.65,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Then I won't tell you, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:06.59,Umaru_Main,onnii,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:10.38,NYK_17:07,kite,0000,0000,0000,,New\NYear's
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:12.50,Umaru_Italics,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,The new year lazily begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.04,0:17:16.59,Umaru_Italics,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what this year will be like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:18.64,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.96,0:17:23.39,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you again this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:29.49,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, same.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:33.15,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what are you counting on me for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.38,0:17:35.77,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you know. Like cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:39.39,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and dinner tonight! I want meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.77,0:17:42.16,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to get any more \Nserious this year, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:44.52,Umaru_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,I did indeed say I was going to get serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:49.90,zawawa_17:42,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Pssst Pssst
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:47.09,Umaru_Main,umar,0000,0000,0000,,However, I never specified a date or...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:48.97,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:23.17,Umaru_Time_Setting,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(251,509)}December 24th
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.35,0:19:36.82,Umaru_Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:37.82,Umaru_Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:39.72,Umaru_Main,kanau,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:45.26,Umaru_Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,She's as hot as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.26,0:19:48.45,Umaru_Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kanau-san's still here, even \Nthough it's Christmas Eve?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.86,0:19:51.72,Umaru_Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say she cares more about \Nwork than Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:58.71,support_19:52,sign,0000,0000,0000,,System Support Section
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.98,0:20:07.61,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,This sucks. I want to go back \Nto how things used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.61,0:20:10.02,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,When we were young and free...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:13.21,Umaru_Main,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't just run away from reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:16.21,Umaru_Main,tai,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, what are \Nyou looking at during work?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.21,0:20:17.98,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:19.05,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Santa suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:20.44,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna wear one with me, Taihei?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:23.66,Umaru_Main,kanau,0000,0000,0000,,It's not going to come the same \Nday you order it, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.00,0:20:25.28,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,True...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.79,0:20:27.97,Umaru_Main,kanau,0000,0000,0000,,Have you finished your checks?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.36,0:20:30.93,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Chief Kanau...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.93,0:20:33.52,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was just taking a little break...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.52,0:20:37.17,Umaru_Main,kanau,0000,0000,0000,,You can quit at any time, A-f-ro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:43.09,Umaru_Main,kanau,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you have any plans today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:45.79,Umaru_Main,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I can't see the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:49.43,Umaru_Main,kanau,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:52.38,Umaru_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like it's Christmas \Ntoday for the rest of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.38,0:20:55.20,Umaru_Main,kanau,0000,0000,0000,,I'd feel bad making you work overtime \Nif you actually have plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:20:58.07,Umaru_Main,tai,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh. No, I don't really have plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.07,0:20:59.82,Umaru_Main,kanau,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.13,0:21:02.56,Umaru_Main,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I just plan on going home, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.56,0:21:04.12,Umaru_Main,kanau,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.35,0:21:11.83,Umaru_Main,kanau,0000,0000,0000,,Then... Um... So you're free, \Neven though it's Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.15,0:21:16.52,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,And you're also here because \Nyou have nothing else to do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:18.60,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Bomber!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.60,0:21:22.76,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,Well, think about it. We're the \Nonly ones here, so who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.40,0:21:25.80,Umaru_Main,kanau,0000,0000,0000,,No one cares, but you piss me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:27.25,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for, Kanau?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.25,0:21:29.81,Umaru_Main,kanau,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm terribly sorry. My hand slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.91,0:21:33.33,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then, Kanau...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:35.42,Umaru_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't the three of \Nus go out like old times?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.42,0:21:36.38,Umaru_Main,kanau,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.28,0:21:53.42,Umaru_Main,kanau,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.82,0:21:56.09,Umaru_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to have dinner \Nwith my family tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.63,0:21:59.74,Umaru_Main,kanau,0000,0000,0000,,You two should also go home and \Nspend tonight with your families.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.32,0:22:10.10,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky break! She said we could go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.26,0:22:16.60,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty rare for Kanau \Nto stop by our section.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.60,0:22:19.35,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,Is it? I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.76,0:22:21.82,Umaru_Main,onii,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, are you renting anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.13,0:22:25.69,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking about renting \Nsomething for my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.69,0:22:27.70,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she's home by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.03,0:22:30.91,Umaru_Main,kanu,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.91,0:22:32.96,Umaru_Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.96,0:22:39.87,Umaru_Main,kanau,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is it so rare for a lone woman \Nto rent a DVD on Christmas Eve?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.23,0:22:42.17,Umaru_Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,No... Your card...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.17,0:22:43.47,Umaru_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.89,0:22:46.55,Umaru_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,They might have Santa outfits \Nat Village Ganvuard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.22,0:22:50.33,Umaru_Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Th-Thank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.06,0:22:50.33,Umaru_Main,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Just how much do you want \Nto wear a Santa outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.32,0:22:59.77,Umaru_Main,kanau,0000,0000,0000,,So cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.46,0:23:22.33,phone_23:20,text,0000,0000,0000,,FROM: Doma Taihei \NAttachment\NMerry Christmas.
