Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.98,0:23:49.04,Umaru_Preview_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have an afro, Bomber?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.04,0:23:50.90,Umaru_Preview_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,What? My philosophy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.90,0:23:54.40,Umaru_Preview_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Let us say my afro reflects my burning soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.40,0:23:57.18,Umaru_Preview_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,So what if some hot lady said she hated afros?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.18,0:23:58.26,Umaru_Preview_Main,bom,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, my afro!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.26,0:24:00.40,Umaru_Preview_Main,umaru,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about a lukewarm soul...
